    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out per the MRL 2 credibility assessment plan for a Class II CPB device. The CFD hemolysis prediction model is accepted as sufficiently credible to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions. Note: this submission conforms to the Minimal profile and does not include a structured Context of Use block; the intended use scope is described narratively in the package description field.",
